---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy" description="How T1 grid handles your data." />
  </head>
  <body class="layout">
    <Header />
    <main class="page-container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>At T1 grid, your privacy is taken seriously. This site uses no tracking or analytics cookies. Functional cookies may be used only where required (e.g. for scheduling via Cal.com or Stripe payments).</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We only use cookies that are necessary to deliver functionality, such as embedded booking or payment systems. These may set cookies when you interact with them.</p>

      <h2>External services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cal.com</strong>: Used for booking calls. May set cookies during scheduling.</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong>: If you make a purchase, Stripe may use functional cookies for secure payment.</li>
        <li><strong>Brevo</strong>: If you sign up for emails, we only use Brevo for form delivery. Tracking is disabled.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Reach out directly to me via <a href="mailto:hello@t1grid.com">hello@t1grid.com</a>.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  }

  h1, h2 {
    font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>
